Version 0.2.0-alpha
2006/01/03

Release Notes: This is the first release with a working "Widgets" module, 
although it has basic features.This release is provided for testing 
and development only!

[+] First release with a working "Widgets" module.
[+] (ALL+GTK2+MSW) Implemented xWidget,xContainer,xWindow,xPanel,xButton,
    xBoxLayout,xFrame,xLabel classes and many others
[+] Added "examples" directory with a first example "hello gui"
[+] Many bug fixes


